      "text": "Fields:\n- id: unique identifier\n- nickname: unique nickname\n- email: unique email\n- password_hash: hashed password\n- first_name\n- last_name\n- age\n- gender\n- created_at: timestamp of registration\n\nConstraints:\n- nickname and email must be unique",
