      "text": "Fields:\n- id: unique identifier for each reaction\n- user_id: the user who reacted\n- post_id: optional, the post reacted to (NULL if it's a comment)\n- comment_id: optional, the comment reacted to (NULL if it's a post)\n- reaction_type: type of reaction, e.g. \"like\", \"dislike\"\n- created_at: timestamp of reaction\n",
